window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>All the retired hero wants to do is...well, it would be nice if he could avoid anything troublesome this time.</b></p> <p>The Retired Hero of Humanity—the man who decided to hide in his woodland cottage after his bloody business was done—is enjoying his life.</p> <p>Jericho really doesn't have plans this time. He's more than happy to just go with the flow. Will the world let him?</p> <p>Garoonie is happy to spend time with him, between her very serious patrols.</p> <p>Giselle is busy most times, but she is having a peaceful time.</p> <p>Orca is still dancing beside the garden patch.</p> <p>Elsewhere, the Demon Realm makes moves as they navigate the fallout of Jericho's actions.</p> <p>The Special Inquiry led by Lougarou heads to the mountains.</p> <p>Refugees leave the Outer Islands for good, helped along by Kiriya and others.</p> <p>Asta is out on vacation, and the Demon Lord is overworked.</p> <p>The Bewitching Realm too, is on the move, with Tomoe heading straight to the cottage to demand answers.</p> <p>Things will, annoyingly, never be the same.</p> <p><i>My Cottage Was Transferred to Another World</i> continues! Here’s what you can expect in this series:</p> <ul> <li>One guy, with multiple fun girls hanging around him.</li> <li>Light Gamelit elements.</li> <li>Retired, Overpowered Protagonist.</li> <li>An extremely loyal wolf girl.</li> <li>Insert Art. A lot of it.</li> <li>Extreme battles and extreme magic.</li> </ul>"; 
